descriptionHtml:
Character preset based on my Nord character, Arielle, made available upon request. The preset can be selected on the character creation menu - it overwrites the first female Nord character preset. The preset can be selected by starting a new game, visiting the face sculptor (assuming you're already a Nord female and have Dawngaurd), or by bringing up the character creation menu in the console - "showracemenu" without quotes. Be aware that if you change your race in this manner, it will mess up your character's stats.




I also use the UNP body style (the armor in the main screenshot is actually CBBE, however). There's a lot of fantastic actor enhancement mods out there, but here's a list of the actor enhancement mods that I use and prefer:

ApachiiSkyHair:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168

No More Blocky Faces (This may get overwritten by "Detailed Faces v2", but I have them both active):
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30

Detailed Bodies (This may get overwritten by "Vanilla skin texture v1_8 4uDIKs RB compatible MAIN FILE", but I have them both active):
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/256

Detailed Faces v2:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26

Detailed Lips:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/689

High Quality Eyes:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/498

Makeup Tweaks:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/23449

DIMONIZED UNP female MAIN body:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709

Vanilla skin texture v1_8 4uDIKs RB compatible MAIN FILE (for reducing neck and hand seams):
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6554

SFW Bikinis for Main body (for eliminating nudity):
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709

The armor featured in the main screenshot is Triss Armor Retextured found here:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4708




COMPATIBILITY:

This mod only overwrites the first female Nord preset during character creation. Any other mod which attempts to do the same thing will be incompatible.




INSTALLATION:

For new installs, copy the "Data" folder to your "Data" folder and activate the esp, or feel free to use NMM (recommended).




PERMISSIONS:

You can do whatever you want with this mod. Just, please give me any due credit.




Be sure to check out my other mods as well:

Rendspire Palace Reborn:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/23134

Rendspire Companions:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/23764

Honeyside Sweetener:
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/20959

Dragon Master Armory
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/56227/
